This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as it deals with intrusion detection, which is a key aspect of cybersecurity. Additionally, the use of Artificial Immune System and Soft Computing techniques further supports this categorization.

The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). 

The use of Soft Computing techniques, which involve the use of fuzzy logic and neural networks, suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
